attributesSection titled “attributes”
Classes in theclassandclassNameJSX attributes are always sorted. Use this option to add more attributes that should be sorted.
functionsSection titled “functions”
If specified, strings in the indicated functions will be sorted. This is useful when working with libraries likeclsxorcva.

